Debian packaging of yacas originally created in 1998 by:
   John Lapeyre <lapeyre@physics.arizona.edu>
and since 2010 improved and maintained by:
   Muammar El Khatib <muammarelkhatib@gmail.com>

This set of debian packaging files was independently created in 2016 by:
   Grzegorz Mazur <teoretyk@gmail.com>
to facilitate building out-of-distribution packages of newer yacas versions

Upstream source:

https://github.com/grzegorzmazur/yacas

